#### Linea de codigo

#### Linea de codigo (Indicar Estilo)

        echo "Hello world!";
    ?>

#### HTML codigo

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <mate charest="utf-8" />
        <title>Hello world!</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Hello world!</h1>
    </body>
</html>
```

<h2>
<li><u>Diagrama 1</u></li>
</h2>

```flow
st=>start: Hola
op=>operation: Hello World
cond=>condition: ¿Si o No?
e=>end: End

st->op->cond
cond(yes)->e
cond(no)->op
```
